sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor App as Application
    participant DI as IServiceProvider
    participant Ctx as SensorContext
    participant EF as Entity Framework Core
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Note over App,DB: Initialisation (pattern DAL)

    App->>DI: GetService SensorContext
    DI-->>App: SensorContext

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over App,DB: Création de la base
        App->>Ctx: Database.EnsureCreated()
        Ctx->>EF: générer le modèle (SensorDAO, SensorValueDAO)
        EF->>DB: CREATE TABLE TBL_Sensor, TBL_SensorValue
        DB-->>App: true si créée
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Note over App,DB: Persistance d'un capteur
        App->>App: new SensorDAO { Name, ConfigJson, ... }
        App->>Ctx: Sensors.Add(sensor)
        App->>Ctx: SaveChanges()
        Ctx->>EF: INSERT
        EF->>DB: INSERT INTO TBL_Sensor
        DB-->>App: Id généré (GUID)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over App,DB: Persistance d'une mesure
        App->>App: new SensorValueDAO { SensorId, ValueJson, ... }
        App->>Ctx: SensorValues.Add(value)
        App->>Ctx: SaveChanges()
        EF->>DB: INSERT INTO TBL_SensorValue (FK_Sensor)
        DB-->>App: mesure enregistrée
    end
